<plot>A visual ballet set to the music of Wagner's Liebestod. Exploration of two female identities (Bulleta/Hellchick). Men are amorphous bulbous creatures (Nella) only capable of experiencing joy through their female counterparts. A tentative resolution is suggested by distant gaze of an older, wiser, sadder figure (Rabbit) who perceives self doubt of the Bulletas destined through experience to become Hellchicks.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?345793</url></doc>
